{"tid":2109992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【防疫不力】港泰護老中心 ４８小時內２名院友去世","createTime":"2020-07-15T14:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T15:18:17.000Z","uid":88743,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"336b6320d0854f998396f17d1191006e8c2c062c","tid":2109992,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"老人家真係好慘<br />\n明明乜都唔可以做<br />\n困係老人院都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1341 (死亡)<br />\n95 歲 女<br />\n本地個案的密切接觸者<br />\n確診日期　2020-07-09<br />\n入住醫院　東區尤德夫人那打素醫院<br />\n現居地　慈雲山<br />\n群組　港泰護老中心<br />\n<br />\n患者有長期病患，為港泰護老中心的院友，7 月 10 日由檢疫中心送院，當時沒有病徵，情況穩定。患者病情於 7 月 11 日轉差，期間需使用 氧氣協助呼吸及藥物治療，治療期間病情持續惡化，於 7 月13 日下午 6 時 31 分離世。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#1350 (死亡)<br />\n90 歲 男<br />\n本地個案的密切接觸者<br />\n確診日期　2020-07-09<br />\n入住醫院　東區尤德夫人那打素醫院<br />\n現居地　慈雲山<br />\n群組　港泰護老中心<br />\n<br />\n患者為港泰護老中心的院友，本身有多種長期病患包括心臟及糖尿病，由檢疫中心送院，沒有病徵。患者於 7 月 15 日因病情惡化於大約下午 4 時 45 分離世。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk/cases\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk%2Fcases&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=9ad4220b\" target=\"_blank\">https://wars.vote4.hk/cases</a>"},{"pid":"e823f58ec1aa2d79cb92ae6c8e5162dadb122953","tid":2109992,"uid":81440,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"九東少咗兩票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ece8e711569f494017f096c7aa1bae2485b6ceb","tid":2109992,"uid":356218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7443ba33e37c1443ee6fbf0a843d2c4bd4f882d3","tid":2109992,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64fbbfa1a71c1c12cd1f5f466863045a1b8650a7